00:09:41.540 --> 00:09:44.960 align:middle line:84%
which would be retailing,
advertising, transportation,

00:09:44.960 --> 00:09:49.400 align:middle line:84%
lawyers, real estate agents,
and financial services--

00:09:49.400 --> 00:09:51.020 align:middle line:90%
could go on and on.

00:09:51.020 --> 00:09:56.640 align:middle line:84%
And manufacturing, which I guess
is pretty self explanatory--

00:09:56.640 --> 00:10:00.140 align:middle line:84%
this entire page
of lecture is just

00:10:00.140 --> 00:10:01.760 align:middle line:90%
meant to be representative.

00:10:01.760 --> 00:10:06.950 align:middle line:84%
