saying is the motivation

00:10:16.520 --> 00:10:19.100 align:middle line:84%
for this is you have
some final demand,

00:10:19.100 --> 00:10:21.230 align:middle line:84%
and how much would
you need to produce

00:10:21.230 --> 00:10:23.720 align:middle line:90%
to satisfy the final demand?

00:10:23.720 --> 00:10:26.360 align:middle line:84%
You could have final
