00:10:45.050 --> 00:10:48.800 align:middle line:84%
services are used in other
sectors, as in this row.

00:10:48.800 --> 00:10:52.880 align:middle line:84%
Services show up in
producing raw materials,

00:10:52.880 --> 00:10:56.090 align:middle line:84%
services show up in
producing services

00:10:56.090 --> 00:10:57.980 align:middle line:84%
because of that
aggregation problem,

00:10:57.980 --> 00:11:00.560 align:middle line:90%
and get used in manufacturing.

00:11:00.560 --> 00:11:03.890 align:middle line:84%
Likewise, if you
go down the column,

00:11:03.890 --> 00:11:07.400 align:middle line:84%
to produce $1 worth
of services, you

00:11:07.400 --> 00:11:10.190 align:middle line:84%
need $0.04 worth
